  <description>
    <p>LocalTranslate is an offline translation application that uses Firefox's neural translation models (from the mozilla/firefox-translations-models project) to perform high-quality translations locally on your device.</p>

    <p>Note: LocalTranslate is not affiliated with The Mozilla Foundation in any way.</p>
    
    <p>LocalTranslate supports the following languages:</p>

